Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.04,Bottom,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:58.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,‎なあ 兆候って？\N
