Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:11.43,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,‎メイン！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:11.68,Bottom,,0000,0000,0000,,Maine!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.31,Bottom,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… Hey.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:14.31,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,‎あの… さ\N
